race.description: Dylan Wight Mp & John Lister Mp Maiden Plate
race.comment: NEVERENOUGHLEGO (5) has had a few chances compared to these but has a bulk of form that have him in the finish here. He was disappointing when beaten as $1.30 at Kilmore but a host of runner up finishes prior read well and we should get a much better price this time around given that market support last time. Wary of the newcomer CUSHIONED (10), a filly by Ghaiyyath on debut for the Freedman yard. She's jumped out well enough on a few occasions and should be ready to go for the top stable. ROGUE WARRIOR (7) hit the line well fresh at Kilmore over 1200m and will appreciate rising in trip here. He's open to improvement at just his third start and has claims. EMANATING (11) is knocking on the door with back to back minor placings. She was sound in third last time at Geelong and should be running on well. ALOISI (4) was solid on debut with scope to improve.
